{
  "id": "RAW_3f60dfdb",
  "title": "从代码到云端：部署 AI 智能体的三个实践教程",
  "url": "https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/from-code-to-cloud-three-labs-for-deploying-your-ai-agent/",
  "date": "2025-12-19 00:00:00",
  "author": "Mollie Pettit",
  "siteName": "Google Cloud Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">You've built a powerful </span><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/discover/what-are-ai-agents\" track-name=\"ai agent\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/discover/what-are-ai-agents\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline\">AI agent</span></a><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">. It works on your local machine, it's intelligent, and it's ready to meet the world. Now, how do you take this agent from a script on your laptop to a secure, scalable, and reliable application in production? On </span><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/\" track-name=\"google cloud\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline\">Google Cloud</span></a><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, there are multiple paths to deployment, each offering a different developer experience.</span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">If you are looking for a detailed architectural comparison to help you choose between </span></p>\n    <div class=\"AjRnyf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md; mouseenter:WOQqYb; mouseleave:Tx5Rb; keydown:duASZc\" jsshadow=\"\" jscontroller=\"Z3eLNd\">\n     <div jsslot=\"\" class=\"WmYQ4d\" jsname=\"kYE3Cd\">\n      <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/run\" track-name=\"cloud run\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/run\" class=\"XQWoyf\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\">Cloud Run</span></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, </span>\n    <div class=\"AjRnyf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md; mouseenter:WOQqYb; mouseleave:Tx5Rb; keydown:duASZc\" jsshadow=\"\" jscontroller=\"Z3eLNd\">\n     <div jsslot=\"\" class=\"WmYQ4d\" jsname=\"kYE3Cd\">\n      <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/kubernetes-engine\" track-name=\"google kubernetes engine (gke)\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/kubernetes-engine\" class=\"XQWoyf\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\">Google Kubernetes Engine (GKE)</span></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, and </span>\n    <div class=\"AjRnyf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md; mouseenter:WOQqYb; mouseleave:Tx5Rb; keydown:duASZc\" jsshadow=\"\" jscontroller=\"Z3eLNd\">\n     <div jsslot=\"\" class=\"WmYQ4d\" jsname=\"kYE3Cd\">\n      <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/products/agent-builder?e=48754805\" track-name=\"vertex ai agent engine\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/products/agent-builder\" class=\"XQWoyf\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\">Vertex AI Agent Engine</span></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, you can start by reading </span><a href=\"https://medium.com/google-cloud/choosing-the-right-deployment-path-for-your-google-adk-agents-86c89c251ab5\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" track-name=\"choosing the right deployment path for your google adk agents\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"medium.com/google-cloud/choosing-the-right-deployment-path-for-your-google-adk-agents-86c89c251ab5\"><strong style=\"text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline\">Choosing the Right Deployment Path for Your Google ADK Agents</strong></a><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">.</span>\n    <p></p>\n    <p><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">Ready to build?</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> As part of our </span><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/production-ready-ai-with-google-cloud-learning-path\" track-name=\"production-ready ai on google cloud learning path\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/production-ready-ai-with-google-cloud-learning-path\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline\">Production-Ready AI on Google Cloud Learning Path</span></a><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, we've created three distinct hands-on labs to help you experience these deployment options for yourself.</span></p>\n    <h2><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">The Managed Solution: Vertex AI Agent Engine</span></h2>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">For teams seeking the </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">simplest path to production</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, </span></p>\n    <div class=\"AjRnyf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md; mouseenter:WOQqYb; mouseleave:Tx5Rb; keydown:duASZc\" jsshadow=\"\" jscontroller=\"Z3eLNd\">\n     <div jsslot=\"\" class=\"WmYQ4d\" jsname=\"kYE3Cd\">\n      <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/products/agent-builder?e=48754805\" track-name=\"vertex ai agent engine\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/products/agent-builder\" class=\"XQWoyf\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\">Vertex AI Agent Engine</span></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> removes the need to manage web servers or containers entirely. It provides an opinionated environment </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">optimized for python agents</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, where you define the agent's logic, and the platform handles the execution, memory, and tool invocation.</span>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"k6ctOd\">\n   <aside class=\"IwVNTb\">\n    <div class=\"ecJG2e nRhiJb-ObfsIf\">\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf nRhiJb-snVHke-ibL1re-X66g3b nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-UFsB2c\">\n      <h4 class=\"Qwf2Db-MnozTc Qwf2Db-MnozTc-OWXEXe-MnozTc-qWD73c\">Start the lab!</h4>\n      <div class=\"nRhiJb-qJTHM nRhiJb-DbgRPb-R6PoUb-ma6Yeb\">\n       <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n        <p><b>Lab</b>: <a href=\"https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/create-multi-agents-adk-a2a\" track-name=\"create multi agent system with adk, deploy in agent engine and get started with a2a protocol\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/create-multi-agents-adk-a2a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"opener\">Create multi agent system with ADK, deploy in Agent Engine and get started with A2A protocol</a>\n         <br></p>\n        <p><b>Objective:</b> <i>Deploy a multi-agent system without provisioning any infrastructure, leveraging built-in capabilities for state management and reasoning while Google manages the runtime.</i></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </aside>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h2><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">The Serverless Experience: Cloud Run</span></h2>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">For teams that want the </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">flexibility of containers</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> without the operational overhead, </span></p>\n    <div class=\"AjRnyf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md; mouseenter:WOQqYb; mouseleave:Tx5Rb; keydown:duASZc\" jsshadow=\"\" jscontroller=\"Z3eLNd\">\n     <div jsslot=\"\" class=\"WmYQ4d\" jsname=\"kYE3Cd\">\n      <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/run\" track-name=\"cloud run\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/run\" class=\"XQWoyf\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\">Cloud Run</span></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> abstracts away the infrastructure, allowing you to deploy your agent as a container that automatically scales up when busy and down to zero when quiet.</span>\n    <p></p>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">This path is particularly powerful if you need to build in </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">languages other than Python</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, use </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">custom frameworks</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, or integrate your agent into existing </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">declarative CI/CD pipelines</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">.</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"k6ctOd\">\n   <aside class=\"IwVNTb\">\n    <div class=\"ecJG2e nRhiJb-ObfsIf\">\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf nRhiJb-snVHke-ibL1re-X66g3b nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-UFsB2c\">\n      <h4 class=\"Qwf2Db-MnozTc Qwf2Db-MnozTc-OWXEXe-MnozTc-qWD73c\">Start the lab!</h4>\n      <div class=\"nRhiJb-qJTHM nRhiJb-DbgRPb-R6PoUb-ma6Yeb\">\n       <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n        <p><b>Lab:</b> <a href=\"https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/production-ready-ai-with-gc/5-deploying-agents/deploy-an-adk-agent-to-cloud-run\" track-name=\"build and deploy an adk agent on cloud run\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/production-ready-ai-with-gc/5-deploying-agents/deploy-an-adk-agent-to-cloud-run\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"opener\">Build and deploy an ADK agent on Cloud Run</a>\n         <br></p>\n        <p><b>Objective:</b> <i>Containerize a tool-using agent with the Google Cloud ADK and deploy it to a secure public HTTPS endpoint to experience the speed of a serverless workflow.</i></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </aside>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h2><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">The Orchestrated Experience: Google Kubernetes Engine (GKE)</span></h2>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">For teams that need </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">precise configuration over their environment</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">, </span></p>\n    <div class=\"AjRnyf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md; mouseenter:WOQqYb; mouseleave:Tx5Rb; keydown:duASZc\" jsshadow=\"\" jscontroller=\"Z3eLNd\">\n     <div jsslot=\"\" class=\"WmYQ4d\" jsname=\"kYE3Cd\">\n      <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/kubernetes-engine\" track-name=\"gke\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/kubernetes-engine\" class=\"XQWoyf\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\">GKE</span></a>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> is designed to manage that complexity. This path shows you how an AI agent functions not just as a script, but as a microservice within a broader orchestrated cluster.</span>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"k6ctOd\">\n   <aside class=\"IwVNTb\">\n    <div class=\"ecJG2e nRhiJb-ObfsIf\">\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf nRhiJb-snVHke-ibL1re-X66g3b nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-UFsB2c\">\n      <h4 class=\"Qwf2Db-MnozTc Qwf2Db-MnozTc-OWXEXe-MnozTc-qWD73c\">Start the lab!</h4>\n      <div class=\"nRhiJb-qJTHM nRhiJb-DbgRPb-R6PoUb-ma6Yeb\">\n       <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n        <p><b>Lab</b>: <a href=\"https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/production-ready-ai-with-gc/5-deploying-agents/deploy-adk-agents-to-gke\" track-name=\"deploy adk agents to google kubernetes engine (gke)\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/production-ready-ai-with-gc/5-deploying-agents/deploy-adk-agents-to-gke\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"opener\">Deploy ADK agents to Google Kubernetes Engine (GKE)</a>\n         <br></p>\n        <p><b>Objective</b>: <i>Deploy an ADK agent into a managed Kubernetes cluster, configuring autoscaling and precise resource limits using industry-standard tooling and manifests.</i></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </aside>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h2><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">Your Path to Production</span></h2>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">Whether you are looking for serverless speed, orchestrated control, or a fully managed runtime, these labs provide the blueprint to get you there.</span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">These labs are part of the </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">Deploying Agents</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> module in our official </span><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/production-ready-ai-with-google-cloud-learning-path\" track-name=\"production-ready ai with google cloud\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/production-ready-ai-with-google-cloud-learning-path\"><strong style=\"text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline\">Production-Ready AI with Google Cloud</strong></a><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"> program. Explore the full curriculum for more content that will help you bridge the gap from a promising prototype to a production-grade AI application.</span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">Share your progress and connect with others on the journey using the hashtag </span><strong style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">#ProductionReadyAI</strong><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\">. Happy learning!&nbsp;</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文介绍了用于通过 Vertex AI Agent Engine、Cloud Run 和 GKE 部署 AI 智能体的三个 Google Cloud 实践教程，为生产级 AI 提供了不同级别的管理和灵活性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文介绍了用于通过 Vertex AI Agent Engine、Cloud Run 和 GKE 部署 AI 智能体的三个 Google Cloud 实践教程，为生产级 AI 提供了不同级别的管理和灵活性。",
  "summary": "本文提供了三个不同的动手实践教程，旨在指导开发者将他们的 AI 智能体从本地脚本部署到 Google Cloud 上的生产就绪应用程序。它概述了三种部署路径：Vertex AI Agent Engine，一个最简单、针对 Python 智能体优化的全托管解决方案；Cloud Run，一个具有容器灵活性的无服务器部署方案，支持各种语言和自定义框架；以及 Google Kubernetes Engine (GKE)，适用于需要精确环境配置和编排微服务的团队。每条路径都提出一个具体的实践教程目标，为将 AI 原型推向生产提供蓝图。文章强调，这些实践教程是“Google Cloud 上的生产就绪 AI 学习路径”的一部分，鼓励进一步探索该课程。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vertex AI Agent Engine 为部署基于 Python 的 AI 智能体提供了最简单的路径。",
      "explanation": "这种全托管解决方案消除了管理 Web 服务器或容器的需要，负责执行、内存和工具调用，为优化的 Python 智能体环境提供支持。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Cloud Run 提供了具有容器灵活性的无服务器部署，支持各种语言。",
      "explanation": "它允许部署可自动扩缩的容器化智能体，使其成为非 Python 语言、自定义框架以及集成到 CI/CD 流水线而不增加运维开销的理想选择。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GKE 为复杂的 AI 智能体部署提供了精确的配置和编排。",
      "explanation": "GKE 专为需要细粒度控制的团队设计，它支持将 AI 智能体作为微服务在编排集群中进行管理，适用于复杂环境需求。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "你已经构建了一个强大的 AI 智能体。它在你的本地机器上运行，具有智能，并且已准备好面向世界。现在，你如何将这个智能体从你笔记本电脑上的一个脚本，转变为一个安全、可扩展且可靠的生产级应用程序？",
    "对于寻求最简单生产路径的团队，Vertex AI Agent Engine 完全消除了管理 Web 服务器或容器的需要。它提供了一个针对 Python 智能体优化的预配置优化环境。",
    "对于那些既希望拥有容器灵活性又不想增加运维开销的团队，Cloud Run 抽象底层基础设施，允许你将智能体部署为容器，在高峰期自动扩展，在空闲时缩减到零。",
    "对于需要对其环境进行精确配置的团队，GKE 旨在管理这种复杂性。这条路径向你展示了 AI 智能体不仅仅是一个脚本，而是一个更广泛的编排集群中的微服务。"
  ],
